<title>Installing the kernel-org Roll</title>

<section id="adding-the-roll" xreflabel="Adding the Roll">
<title>Adding the Roll</title>

<para>

The kernel-org Roll can be installed during the Frontend installation step
or may be added afterwards with <computeroutput>rocks add roll</computeroutput>

</para>


<para>
	
The kernel-org Roll is added to a Frontend installation in exactly the same
manner as the required HPC Roll.  Specifically, after the HPC Roll is
added the installer will once again ask if you have a Roll (see
below).  Select 'Yes' and insert the kernel-org Roll.

<screenshot>
	<graphic fileref="images/i-01.png" scale=50></graphic>
</screenshot>

</para>


</section>


